Laud Anoo Konadu (amụrụ na Mee 25, 1992), nke a maara dị ka Dancegod Lloyd, bụ onye na-agba egwú, onye nkuzi ịgba egwú, na onye na-eme ihe nkiri na Ghana. Ọ bụ onye guzobere ụlọ akwụkwọ ịgba egwú, DWP academy
N'afọ 2020, ọ rụrụ ọrụ na vidiyo egwu "Already" nke Beyonce, nke gosipụtara Shatta Wale.
A mụrụ Laud Anoo Konadu na 25 Mee 1992 n'obodo a na-akpọ Kibi na mpaghara ọwụwa anyanwụ nke Ghana
Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na Solidarity International School ma mesịa gaa Presbyterian Boys Senior High School na Accra. A mụrụ ya na Maazị Theophilus Konadu, nna ya na Oriakụ
Ọ rụrụ ọrụ na ọtụtụ vidiyo egwu, gụnyere "Already" nke Beyonce, "See Brother" nke Patoranking, na "Shoo" nke Kwamz na Flava.

N'afọ 2017, Dancegod na onye njikwa ya, Quables, na onye na-agba egwu, Afro Beast, malitere otu ọrụ ebere a na-akpọ "Dance With Purpose Academy", nke ebumnuche ya bụ inyere ndị na-eto eto, ndị na-agba egwú nwere nkà aka n'okporo ámá. Dance with Purpose Academy nwere ndị na-agba egwú dị ka Endurance Grand, Richael, Real Cesh, Energetic Tymlez, Demzy Baye, Lisa Quam na Afronitaaa. Ndị a bụ ndị na-agba egwú a ma ama, n'ime ihe karịrị ma ọ bụ ihe na-erughị ndị na- ịgba egwú 200 debanyere aha na Dwp Academy; enwere ọtụtụ ndị ọzọ n'ebe ahụ.
Shoo - bụ abụ nke Kwamz na Flava mana a na-ekwu na Dancegod Lloyd mepụtara usoro ịgba egwú.
